# Database configuration (Prisma Backend)
# 🥋 OSS SENSEI: Use a String de Conexão (URI) do Supabase com o Pooler (Porta 6543).
# Formato: postgresql://postgres.[PROJECT-REF]:[PASSWORD]@[REGION].pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres?pgbouncer=true&connection_limit=1
# ⚠️ IMPORTANTE: Se sua senha tiver @, #, !, use URL Encoding (@ -> %40, # -> %23).
# EXÊMPLO: DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres.abc123xyz:senha123@aws-1-us-west-1.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres?pgbouncer=true&connection_limit=1"
